msgid "When enabled, sunnypilot will attempt to manage the built-in cruise control buttons by emulating button presses for limited longitudinal control."
msgstr "启用后，sunnypilot 将尝试通过模拟按钮按压来管理内置巡航控制按钮，以实现有限的纵向控制。"

