msgstr "选择 {}"

msgid "If you're driving at 20 mph (32 km/h) or below and have your blinker on, the car will plan a turn in that direction at the nearest drivable path. This prevents situations (like at red lights) where the car might plan the wrong turn direction."
msgstr "如果您以 20 mph (32 km/h) 或更低的速度行驶并打开了转向灯，车辆将在最近的可行驶路径上规划转向。这可以防止车辆规划错误转向方向的情况（例如在红灯前）。"


msgid "Enable this for the car to learn and adapt its steering response time. Disable to use a fixed steering response time. Keeping this on provides the stock openpilot experience."
msgstr "启用此功能以让车辆学习并调整其转向响应时间。禁用以使用固定的转向响应时间。保持开启可获得原版 openpilot 体验。"


msgid "When enabled, sunnypilot will attempt to manage the built-in cruise control buttons. This allows the user to maintain full control over longitudinal control while benefiting from sunnypilot's lateral control."
msgstr "启用后，sunnypilot 将尝试管理内置巡航控制按钮。这允许用户在保持对纵向控制的完全控制的同时，受益于 sunnypilot 的横向控制。"


msgid "Chevron: Enable or disable the chevron display, showing the path that the car is planning to take."
msgstr "箭头：启用或禁用箭头显示，显示车辆计划行驶的路径。"


msgid "Path: Enable or disable the path display, showing the road edges and lane lines detected by the car."
msgstr "路径：启用或禁用路径显示，显示车辆检测到的道路边缘和车道线。"


msgid "Show blind spot warnings when a vehicle is detected in the blind spot."
msgstr "当在盲区检测到车辆时显示盲区警告。"

